I spent like an hour trying to find the right song for this video and it’s still cheesy af since I did it on my phone 😐 This was originally a ring and tbh after seeing it printed Im gonna go back and redesign a band onto it instead of a chain slide bail bc I didn’t like how tiny it was for a necklace so bear with me as I perfect it’s conception. However! Fun fact- I actually used to edit videos professionally and get pretty lost with all the layers/effects/transitions ect but I traded my MacBook Pro for this dope gaming RAZER laptop plus some cash so I could CAD on the go like a real boy but I hate windows user face since I’ve been team apple, so now I don’t ever edit/ indulge in my real videography programs because it’s a different workflow I haven’t tapped into yet but I’m gonna try to make more visual content showcasing my art and ze process. That trade off was the mark of an era where I decided to truly invest and risk my prized possessions in hope this would have a better return. So far so good ;) thank you lovely people for supporting this vision. Making cosmic adornments + everlasting treasures while exploring my imagination/creativity has just begun❣️I love u @thriftworks @gemvisioncorp @envisiontec @razer ... wonder how it feels to see me blossom in the very mud you buried me in??💀🖤🥀✨✨ #lotusflowerbomb
